translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,123,"Hini na nina bakholwayo balweni abo bangakholwayo bazizizalwana zenu, mabafumane ubungqwabalala kuni; bazi kananjalo okokuba uAllâh ukunye nabamoyikayo"
  9,124,"Qho xa kufika iSûrah abanye babo bathi: “Ngubani ke owongezeleleke ukholo lwakhe yiyo?” Ke bona abo bakholwayo, iyalongezelela ukholo lwabo yaye banochulumanco"
  9,125,"Ke bona abo iintliziyo zabo zinesifo, iya kongeza izikrokro neentandabuzo kwizikrokro zabo, nokungakholwa nokuthandabuza, baze bafe besengabangakholwayo"
  9,126,"Ababoni na ukuba bafakwa elucikidweni kube kanye okanye kube kabini enyakeni, kodwa abajiki babuye ngenguquko, bengafundi nasifundo (kolo cikido)"
  9,127,"Maxa onke kufika iSûrah bayana ngamehlo: (besithi omnye komnye) “Ingaba ukhona na onibonayo?” Baze bafulathele bemke. Ke kaloku uAllâh Uzigqwethile iintliziyo zabo kuba bangabantu abangaqiqiyo"
  9,128,"Inene ufikile kuni uMthunywa (uMuhammad) ephuma phakathi kwenu. Iyamkhathaza yena into yokuba nifumane umonzakalo okaye ubunzima. Yena unenkathalo ngani, kumakholwa uzele lusizi, imfesane, nenceba"
  9,129,"Kodwa ukuba bayatshikila bemke, yithi (Muhammad) uAllâh Wanele Eyedwa kum. Akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe. Mna ndibeka ithemba lam kuYe kwaye Yena yiNkosi yeTrone yaMandla"